  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>うわぁ〜。
ホットドッグのお詫びに
こんなにおいしいパンをくれるなんて</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wow〜! To think he'd give us such delicious
bread as an apology for the hotdog.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとう！
これで怒られないですむよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you!
Now he won't get angry.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>20</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>マジうっめぇな、このパン♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This bread is seriously tasty! ♪</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだ！
お前、俺の屋敷でパン職人として働けよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you know what!
You can work at my mansion as a baker!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>16</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>断る。
俺は海の上が性に合ってるんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'll have to refuse. I'm best suited to the sea.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>それに……パン職人は
朝が早いらしいからな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Plus... bakers gotta get up
too early in the morning...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんなに寝たいのか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Do you really need to sleep that much...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
